UNDER CONTRACT
Luxury Family Home with Six Bedrooms for Extended Family !!!
Excellent Large Family Home with the lot
Situated in an excellent location in THE HOT Dandenong Area!
Home buyers and investors alike will score this amazing unique property a 10 out of 10 on location and presentation....
Positioned in a family friendly quiet court location, this property is suitable for a large family home, or with an opportunity to live in one residence and receive a rental income from the other home...
FRONT HOUSE
This lovely home at the front comprises a landscaped front garden upon entry with 5 good sized bedrooms with built in robes, the master bedroom is complete with a full ensuite and lounge-retreat area, delightful country style kitchen with a fast & efficient induction cooking system, open plan living with polished timber floor boards, large lounge area, gas ducted heating, air conditioning units for climate control, cable tv, internet, 1.5kw solar system plus lots more....
Outside consists of a secure & private paved courtyard area with grass courtyard including a laserlite covered pergola, plus large lock up garage.
SELF CONTAINED UNIT AT REAR with Disabilty Access
This beautiful property at the rear comprises a 1-bedroom self-contained unit complete with ensuite bathroom, modern kitchen with dishwasher, open plan meals area, lounge area, European laundry, heating / air conditioning unit for comfort, plus additional extras...
Outside consists of a pattern paved concrete alfresco area upon entry, complete with a private rear backyard garden area & completed with a 10,000lt water tank, vegetable patches, established fruit trees, & brick paving bbq entertainment area. Ideal for parents -teenage retreat / office / gym area / property rental / air bnb etc.
This property will be sold with vacant possession making it suitable for both owner occupiers or investors wanting to immediately lease the property for additional income $.
250 metres to Bus Stop, 300 metres to Vet, 500 metres to Dandenong High School, 700 metres to Dandenong West Primary School, 800 metres to Local IGA Supermarket and Shopping Precinct, 800 metres to St Gerard’s Catholic School, 1.1 K’s to Dandenong Market, 1.2 K’s to Dandenong Hospital

Make an appointment to view this property! With so much to offer - this property has huge potential!
A GOLD addition for any professional investor’s portfolio!

Description:
Potential, value for money, own half block (over 400m2)
Private inspections only'
Set on a large allotment, this two-bedroom brick veneer villa is a great value for your money!
This is a rare opportunity to own this kind of property, with 407sqm approx - two on the block plus no active body corporate. This hidden treasure consists of generous size lounge with large windows.
Updated kitchen with solid wood benchtop, splashback, rangehood, gas stove and electric oven, LG dishwasher and a meal area. Decent size bedrooms with BIRs. Air-conditioner in main bedroom and gas wall heater set in the lounge. Separate bathroom, toilet and laundry. Beautiful floating floorboard all around, and tiled in wet areas. Large windows in living and kitchen areas overlook a huge and cosy backyard.
The secure and private backyard has plenty of room for the kids, pets, relaxation and/or potential to extend an extra room or two if required (STCA).
Minutes away from Dandenong West Primary school, local shops, train stations, Hemmings Park and East Link and much more. For private inspection or more information, please contact Art Sudharm on 0403 571 245.

Description:
Enviable elegance in Dandenong central
Decadent designer details and generous internal dimensions fuse together in perfect unison throughout this unique single level home, delivering a lifestyle of ease for the busy family, contemporary couple, downsizer or investor.
Benefitting from a brilliant street front position, the home's enticing verandah offers a welcome introduction, opening onto a magnificent lounge room that's large enough to host movie nights and complemented by decorative 9-foot ceilings.
Indulging the avid chef, the gourmet kitchen/meals zone showcases sparkling stone benches, Bosch/Blanco appliances, Bosch dishwasher, corner pantry plus a spectacular island breakfast bench that offers ample space for every family member.
Designed to keep cooking odours at bay, sliding doors open onto a rear dining zone and 2nd kitchen that's taken the place of the courtyard and could easily be converted back for those who prefer an outdoor area.
A pleasing surprise for families, there are four robed bedrooms; master with ensuite, accompanied by a bathroom with toilet, laundry taps and easy-clean floor-to-ceiling tiles.
Adorned with the desired extras of a high-end, ducted heating/refrigerated air conditioning unit, alarm system, ceiling roses plus a double garage with internal access and a remote gated driveway.
In a dream location, walking distance to Dandenong Plaza, buses, trains, Dandenong Market, Dandenong Hospital, Dandenong Primary, St John's College and Dandenong High, near Monash and EastLink Freeways.

Description:
SOLD AT AUCTION BY DINESH RAGHU
Enjoying an outstanding location in Dandenong, this two bedroom unit is the perfect smart start that will also become a great future investment. Centrally positioned between parklands, recreation amenities and Dandenong CBD youll simply love the lifestyle on offer.
Greeted by an impressively high ceiling, timber style flooring and large windows, the home has an immediately light, airy and inviting feel. A kitchen, meals and living area form the open plan living zone whilst two bedrooms, a bathroom, laundry, reverse cycle air conditioner and wall heater provide comfort and convenience.

Description:
New Paint and New Price!
Sale By Set Date: Tuesday 30th April at 5pm (unless sold prior)
With only a hop skip and a jump to the nearest shops, parks, walking tracks and bus stops this large unit, set amongst high quality other properties, is in a hot location close to all of Dandenongs amenities including its most popular schools, Dandenong Plaza, and freeways. This home has everything a downsizers, first home buyer or investor would need!
This lovely 3 bedroom has been well maintained and upgraded to meet the needs of the former owners. With an incredibly spacious open plan living area, complete with large split system air conditioning, you'll never have to worry about the oppressive heat in summer again. Each of the bedrooms comes off this living space and provides easy living for the new owners. The high ceilings give the feeling of more space and theres plenty of room for furniture or the opportunity to place your own stamp on this lovely home.
Outside you've got an undercover area thats close to the kitchen, making entertaining a breeze. The remote double garage is a massive bonus as many properties in the group only have one. With ducted vacuum and heating, fans in a number of the rooms, spa in the bathroom and lovely boxed windows, this delightful property will surely please all who enter.
